  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0bb9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb7 \u0b9f\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Attack on protestors is condemnable - Harsha de Silva",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "I strongly condemn the attack by the security forces on the early morning Khali protestors.",
        "Harsha de Silva, Member of Parliament of United People's Shakti, said that it is not acceptable for the President to use the power obtained in the Parliament without the support of the Lok Sabha for repression.",
        "The early morning attack on the protestors is a stain on the country. It will lead our country further to the abyss.",
        "I still support a peaceful and fair struggle. We will continue to support. However I do not agree with the abusive and oppressive behavior of some who claim to be protesting. Because of this, we cannot condone such activities that people do not approve of.",
        "Only peaceful struggle should continue. In this case, I again condemn the attack on the protestors in the morning.",
        "And it is not acceptable for the President to use the power vested in the Parliament without the support of the Lok Sabha in this way for repression",
        "He said that if President Ranil Wickremesinghe has a real desire to save this country, he should appoint an all-party government and hold elections in Parliament next March to reflect the will of the people."
      ],
